OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,FThe first duty of a government is to
OL,7,Fdefend the country, Sir Alex Younger,
OL,8,Fthe former MI6 chief, told ITV News
OL,9,FGlobal Security Editor Rohit Kachroo
OL,11,FIt is the moment when any incoming
OL,12,Fprime minister is forced to think of
OL,13,Fthe magnitude of their new role.
OL,15,FFollowing long weeks of campaigning -
OL,16,Fof baby-holding and handshakes - the
OL,17,Fwriting of 'the letters of last
OL,18,Fresort' is when it becomes clear that
OL,19,Frunning the country is about more than
OL,20,Fmere politics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
