OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,FIf Labour wins the General Election,
OL,7,Fone of Sir Keir Starmer's early tasks
OL,8,Fwill be to handwrite a letter to
OL,9,FBritain's nuclear submarine commanders
OL,10,Finstructing them how to respond to an
OL,11,Fattack which has potentially killed
OL,12,Fhim and wiped out the UK.
OL,14,F"I know that's been the case for his
OL,15,Fpredecessors, where suddenly the
OL,16,Fgravity of what he has volunteered
OL,17,Ffor, when you think about the
OL,18,Fenormity," says Sir Alex Younger, the
OL,19,Fformer MI6 chief.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
