OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"The first duty of a government is to
OL,7,Fdefend the country, so as is famous,
OL,8,Fhe'll be confronted with the need to
OL,9,Fthink about the instructions that he
OL,10,Fgives to our Royal Navy submarines
OL,11,Fcarrying the deterrent.
OL,13,F"And I suspect he's been very busy
OL,14,Fthinking about stuff.
OL,16,F"If it is Keir Starmer, that will be a
OL,17,Fmoment. He'll be given advice on what
OL,18,Fto put in that letter, but it is his
OL,19,Fresponsibility and his alone."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
