OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,FBut for Sir Alex, who saw the greatest
OL,7,Fglobal security threats to the UK
OL,8,F"from the inside" during six years
OL,9,Frunning the Secret Intelligence
OL,10,FService, this will be the start of a
OL,11,Fdecade of international challenges
OL,12,Ffacing whoever wins the election.
OL,14,FThey would face unpredictable
OL,15,Fconflicts in Ukraine, the Middle East,
OL,16,Fand potentially the Far East.
OL,18,FBut, in Sir Alex's view, Britain's
OL,19,Fvoice will be reduced because it has
OL,20,Fmade itself "irrelevant" thanks to
OL,21,FBrexit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
