OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our Election
OL,7,FBriefing newsletter here for exclusive
OL,8,Fand original campaign coverage from
OL,9,FITV News. Direct to your inbox at 5pm
OL,10,Fevery weekday
OL,12,F"Since I've left office and I've
OL,13,Ftravelled around Europe, I am
OL,14,Fprofoundly depressed. Nobody mentions
OL,15,Fthe UK.
OL,17,F"We've just made ourselves irrelevant.
OL,18,FAnd this is extraordinary," he says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
