OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"At the beginning part of this
OL,7,Fcentury, we were the dominant force.
OL,8,FFrance has effectively eclipsed that
OL,9,Fand, and we just, you just don't hear
OL,10,Fa discussion of us. And I think Brexit
OL,11,Fhas marginalised us."
OL,13,FSir Alex says he is "worried" about
OL,14,FDonald Trump returning to office in
OL,15,Fthe US elections in November.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
