OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"What's the thing that we do that
OL,7,Fautocratic regimes don't do? We make
OL,8,Falliances and we have a separation of
OL,9,Fpowers within our countries that make
OL,10,Four governments accountable. I think
OL,11,Fon both those issues, Donald Trump
OL,12,Ftakes a different approach."
OL,14,FAlthough he commends the former
OL,15,Fpresident's efforts in forcing
OL,16,FEuropean allies to increase their
OL,17,Fdefence spending after years of "free-
OL,18,Friding", he says whoever becomes prime
OL,19,Fminister should seek to persuade Trump
OL,20,Fof the value of its Western security
OL,21,Falliances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
