OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"My message to Donald Trump, if I was
OL,7,Fthe next prime minister, would be that
OL,8,FAmerica is not being done over. It's a
OL,9,Fprime beneficiary of the international
OL,10,Fsystem that it's set up and its
OL,11,Fwillingness to police globalisation.
OL,12,FWhilst I can see that is onerous and
OL,13,Fexpensive, it's profoundly beneficial."
OL,15,FBut, he predicts, whoever wins the
OL,16,FGeneral Election on Thursday will have
OL,17,Fa decade to face down the Russian
OL,18,Fthreat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
