OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"If we don't do it in 10 years, I
OL,7,Fthink we're going to put our kids in a
OL,8,Fposition of extraordinary
OL,9,Fvulnerability for which they will not
OL,10,Fthank us."
OL,12,FAnd responding to claims by Nigel
OL,13,FFarage that the EU and NATO provoked
OL,14,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine, he said
OL,15,Fhe agreed to part of the Reform UK
OL,16,Fleader's argument but rejected the
OL,17,Fsubstance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
