OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"It may surprise you, but I half agree
OL,7,Fwith him. We absolutely did provoke
OL,8,FRussia. But the catch is that we
OL,9,Fprovoked Russia not through our
OL,10,Fstrength, but through our weakness. It
OL,11,Fwas our serial weakness that led us to
OL,12,Fwhere we are today."
OL,14,F"That's where the rubber hits the
OL,15,Froad. We are all human beings, we have
OL,16,Fbasic needs, for food and love and all
OL,17,Fof these things. But perhaps the most
OL,18,Ffundamental is protection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
