OL,3,CFormer MI6 chief: Next PM will be hit
OL,4,Cby the 'gravity' of the role
OL,6,F"And for good or ill, and however
OL,7,Frealistic this is or not, we reside
OL,8,Fthose hopes in our government. And if,
OL,9,Fif the government seemed to falter in
OL,10,Fthat space, the effects on our
OL,11,Fconfidence and national mood are
OL,12,Falmost instant."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
